message: Dear Bob, I am excited to present our premium product to you. This exceptional item has been meticulously crafted and holds significant value to us at $12,000. Given its worth and the unique benefits it offers, we believe it would be a valuable addition to your collection or business. We are offering this product to you at an exclusive price of $9,500, hoping to provide you with a special opportunity. Please let us know if you're interested in exploring this offer further.
